ygData.messageBody:
I've heard that as soon as the boat enters the Butcherblock zone, if you
jump off and swim straight down (the dead spot is what I call it because the
boat just sits there. I assume it's to make sure all the players on the boat
are synched) you will fall through the world. It will then take you to near
the Kaladim entrance. (I believe that's what I was told)
